g.aria-label: "par_name::parameter.file_suffix | change = change_type | condition A | condition B"
Parameter name (optional) The user can define a unique parameter name. If a name is defined it must be separated with '::'
SWAT parameter (required) The SWAT parameter name and the suffix of the file where this parameter is found must be provided.
Separator (required) All definitions are separated by a pipe ope- rator '|'
Type of change (required) change types are: - (absolute value) - (absolute change) - (percent change) - (relative change)
Conditions (optional) Conditions can be added to constrain parameter changes e.g.spatially or ty- pologically
